blog.description: Hi! I'm Jessica. Proud mother to Veronica Belle, a beautiful cockapoo. I married the king of my heart on September 13th, 2015. I have a slight obsession with Taylor Swift. I also love all things Disney. I would love to meet Taylor one day and tell her how she helped me get through some of the hardest parts of my life. I have been a fan of hers since 2007!

body:

summary: Yesterday I was out to lunch with my girlfriends in my hometown and guess what we came across?! This amazing umbrella...
body:
Yesterday I was out to lunch with my girlfriends in my hometown and guess what we came across?! This amazing umbrella installation that screamed Me!

It immediately made me think of the BBMA performance and so of course we had to stop and take photos. It still ceases to amaze me how everywhere I go little things make me think of @taylorswift. Somehow I feel like she’s with me even though she’s probably jet setting around the world.

Taylor- just hope you know how much light you bring to my life even in the smallest of ways. Hope you’re having a fabulous day wherever you are ☺️
